<div style="width: 600px; max-width: 100%; margin: 0 auto;">
  <% date = "APRIL #{@competitor.youth? ? '12TH' : '13TH'}, 2019" %>
  <%
    case @competitor.selected_comp
    when "Both"
      time = @competitor.youth? ? "3:00pm & 5:00pm" : "11:30am & 2:00pm"
    when "Speed Comp"
      time = @competitor.youth? ? "3:00pm" : "5:00pm"
    when "Freestyle Comp"
      time = @competitor.youth? ? "11:30am" : "2:00pm"
    end
  %>
  <% date_and_time = [date, time].join(" at ") %>
  <p>Hello,</p>
  <p>Thank you for Registering for the FitCon 2019 <%= @competitor.age_group.to_s.titleize %> Parkour <%= @competitor.selected_comp == "Both" ? "Freestyle & Speed Comp" : @competitor.selected_comp %> Competition to be held on <%= date_and_time %> at the Salt Palace Convention Center during FitCon. We're really excited to have you attend and throw down!! This email is to serve as a confirmation that we received your registration for <span style="color: #DF0D15;"><%= @competitor.full_name %></span> and to inform you that we are finalizing your registration.</p>
  <p>As a quick reminder those who participate in the competition will also get into FitCon for free during both days. <span style="color: #DF0D15;"><%= @competitor.full_name %></span> will be randomly assigned a time during the competition and if they qualify for finals will be able to compete in the final round at the end of the competition.</p>
  <p>There is also a mandatory Athlete meeting on Thursday, April 11 where they will receive their FitCon wristband and competitor shirt. Details about that meeting will follow in the confirmation email to be sent after your registration is finalized.</p>
  <p>If you have any questions feel free to respond to this email or reach out to us on facebook.</p>
  <p>See you at the competition!</p>
  <br>
  <p>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ryan Sannar<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Manager<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Parkour Utah<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="tel:8444355867">844-435-5867</a>
  </p>
</div>
